{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/03/11/apt添加代理.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e5a8de66-aa6c-56d4-ae8a-d6b5f178eb17","excerpt":"为 apt 添加代理 我的上帝啊，这两天都在忙活代理（翻译腔）。 系统全局下的似乎对 apt 无效，需要单独设置。 增加代理","html":"<h1>为 apt 添加代理</h1>\n<p>我的上帝啊，这两天都在忙活代理（翻译腔）。</p>\n<p>系统全局下的<code class=\"language-text\">http_proxy</code>似乎对 apt 无效，需要单独设置。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">nano</span> /etc/apt/apt.conf.d/proxy.conf</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>增加代理</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">Acquire <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  HTTP::proxy <span class=\"token string\">\"http://127.0.0.1:8080\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  HTTPS::proxy <span class=\"token string\">\"http://127.0.0.1:8080\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/apt添加代理.html","date":"March 11, 2020","title":"apt添加代理"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/apt添加代理.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/使用docker安装Jenkins.html","title":"使用docker安装Jenkins"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/snap添加代理.html","title":"snap添加代理"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}